{"lemma":"صَنائِعِ","slug":"صَنائِعِ","root":"ص.ن.ع","root_slug":"ص-ن-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ن-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25017","n25022"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%90%D8%B9%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَنَعَ (ṣanaʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"art, skill"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"occupation, profession"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"handicraft"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"trade, craft"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"manufacture"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"industry"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of صَنَعَ (ṣanaʕa, “to make, manufacture”)."},"ipa":["/sˤi.naː.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25017","headword_ar":"صِنَاعَةٌ","root":"SnE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanoEapN","text_ar":"صَنْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places. The saying of 'Alee,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^oxa*u mino kul~i SinaAEapK SinaAEatuhu","text_ar":"يُوْخَذُ مِنْ كُلِّ صِنَاعَةٍ صِنَاعَتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", if correctly related, means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^oxa*u mino kul~i *iY SinaAEapK maSonuwEuhu","text_ar":"يُوْخَذُ مِنْ كُلِّ ذِى صِنَاعَةٍ مَصْنُوعُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"From every one possessing skill in manufacture should be taken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"procured, that which he has manufactured:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or perhaps"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano","text_ar":"عَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from every craftsman is to be acquired his craft"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n25022","headword_ar":"صَنَّاعَةٌ","root":"SnE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SinoEN","text_ar":"صِنْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", former half."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}